# Scenario Descriptions
showcase.scenario.happy.desc=Tests the standard successful flow where all steps in all phases complete without error.
showcase.scenario.happy.expect=Expected: PREPARE phase (Step A & B) succeeds -> COMMIT phase (Step A & B) succeeds -> Transaction COMPLETED.
showcase.scenario.retry.desc=Tests automatic retry logic. Step B is configured to fail twice with a retryable error before succeeding.
showcase.scenario.retry.expect=Expected: Step B will show "retrying" twice, then eventually succeed. Transaction COMPLETED.
showcase.scenario.compensation.desc=Tests backward recovery (Saga Compensation). Step B fails with a non-retryable error during Prepare phase.
showcase.scenario.compensation.expect=Expected: Step B fails -> Engine initiates COMPENSATE phase -> Step A & B compensated -> Transaction FAILED (Consistent).
showcase.scenario.commit_failure.desc=Tests failure during the Commit phase. Step B fails after successfully preparing.
showcase.scenario.commit_failure.expect=Expected: Prepare phase succeeds -> Commit starts -> Step B fails -> Compensation initiated (if backward recovery) -> Transaction FAILED (or Suspended based on strategy).
showcase.scenario.partial_group.desc=Tests partial failure within a parallel step group. Step B and C execute concurrently; C fails while B succeeds.
showcase.scenario.partial_group.expect=Expected: Step A succeeds -> Group 2 runs (B & C) -> C fails -> Compensation initiated for A and B.
showcase.scenario.suspended.desc=Tests manual intervention. A failure occurs during the Compensation phase, leaving the system in an inconsistent state.
showcase.scenario.suspended.expect=Expected: Prepare fails -> Compensate starts -> Compensate fails -> Transaction SUSPENDED. Requires manual fix.
showcase.scenario.timeout.desc=Tests global transaction timeout. Step B is configured to hang, exceeding the allocated time for the step.
showcase.scenario.timeout.expect=Expected: Step B times out -> Engine detects timeout -> Compensation initiated -> Transaction FAILED.
showcase.scenario.custom.desc=Manual fault injection mode. Configure individual step behaviors using the panels below.
showcase.scenario.custom.expect=Expected: Dependent on your configuration.

